trans-unit.source: A report that indicates users who have successfully signed in to your directory from an anonymous proxy IP address.
trans-unit.target: A report that indicates users who have successfully signed in to your directory from an anonymous proxy IP address.

trans-unit.source: <html></html>This report indicates users who have successfully signed in to your directory while assigned a client IP address that has been recognized by Microsoft as an anonymous proxy IP address (Tor IP).These proxies are often used by users that want to hide their computer’s IP address, and may be used for malicious intent.<html></html><html></html> Results from this report will show the number of times a user successfully signed in to your directory from that address and the proxy’s IP address.<html></html>
